1013.long_description:
***Note:*** This error relates to the Martini patches, which are now deprecated.

The patcher failed to restore a file from its backup. The patched file remains in place.
1013.long_solution: Reboot your console and try again. If the issue persists, this is most likely a bug in the Martini patcher - please get in touch with a developer on our [Discord](https://discord.gg/pretendo).
